        </div>
        <div class="form-container">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>RaiseIT is a Student Complaint and Grievance Management System designed to provide students with a transparent, efficient, and fair platform to raise concerns and track their resolution.</p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To empower students by giving them a voice and ensuring their grievances are addressed in a timely and professional manner by the appropriate staff members.</p>
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p>Students can submit complaints through our secure portal, track the status of their complaints using a unique reference number, and receive updates as their case progresses through our resolution pipeline.</p>
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <p>Anonymous submissions, priority-based handling, multi-department routing, real-time status tracking, and secure role-based access for students, staff, and administrators.</p>
        </div>
